Selected repository: imhaozi/imhaozi.github.io
Permissions: 添加Contents，然后改成Read and write，Metadata默认只读，不用管&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0"&gt;
